descriptionHtml:
RR Octavia Set for UNP v1.1


[Introduction]
 This MOD adds Weapons & Armors from A certain game.

 
[Contents]
 One-hand Sword           3Colors
 Coat                     3Colors
 Gloves                   2Colors
 Boots                    3Colors
 Belt(Calves)             3Colors

  These are equipment equivalent to "Elven equipment".
  These production and strengthening are almost the same as "Elven equipment".



[Installation]
 overwrite Meshes and Textures folder,and esp file /Skyrim/Data/
 and activate esp file.


[Location]
 Entrance of Whiterun town.
 These enter the chest near the rampart.


[Recommendation]
 Crean Installation is recommended.
 Because trash is left.

 
[At the end]
 Please use these when good though these are not so good.
 The modification and the re-distribution of these files
 are prohibited.
 I wish to express my gratitude to Skyrim and you.
 Enjoy!


[History]
 1.1 Weight modified
     Texture modified
     Mesh modified

 1.0 Mod released



 Presented by Reira
